## Monitoring & Logging

### 1. PM2 Monitoring

```bash
# Real-time monitoring
pm2 monit

# View logs
pm2 logs aleph-dashboard --lines 100

# View error logs only
pm2 logs aleph-dashboard --err

# Clear logs
pm2 flush

# View process information
pm2 info aleph-dashboard

