- `redis_del` - Delete key
- `redis_keys` - List keys by pattern
- `redis_lpush` - Push to list (left)
- `redis_rpush` - Push to list (right)
- `redis_lpop` - Pop from list (left)
- `redis_rpop` - Pop from list (right)
- `redis_zadd` - Add to sorted set
