mkdir -p lib
git mv auth_middleware.py lib/
git mv config.py lib/
# ... update imports ...
```
```

### Example 3: Python Simple Scan

```bash
python3 lib/scanners/timeout_detector.py ~/code/myproject
```

**Output:**
